# Download Banner Bottom Padding

Every scrollable page container must account for the fixed desktop download banner (`DesktopDownloadBanner`) which sits at `position: fixed; bottom: 0` with a height of 56px.

## Pattern

```tsx
import {
  useIsDesktopDownloadBannerVisible,
  DESKTOP_BANNER_HEIGHT,
} from '@/features/download-banner';

const isDesktopBannerVisible = useIsDesktopDownloadBannerVisible();

<div
  style={{
    paddingBottom: isDesktopBannerVisible ? DESKTOP_BANNER_HEIGHT + 24 : undefined,
  }}
>
  {/* page content */}
</div>
```

The formula is `DESKTOP_BANNER_HEIGHT + 24` (56 + 24 = 80px) when visible. This gives the banner height plus 24px breathing room.

For fixed-position elements at the bottom, offset their `bottom` value by `DESKTOP_BANNER_HEIGHT` instead.

